h payment per the terms noted on your quote. Defer to the last page of your quote for payment details and your preferred method of payment.</span><br clear="none" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.3333px;"><br>Please note the following shipping terms and conditions:</div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">1. We do not directly export from the USA.   But we ship your order to your&nbsp;</span></font></div><span class="im" style="color: rgb(80, 0, 80);"><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">designated USA freight forwarder.   Then your USA freight forwarder exports your order to&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">your ship to destination.  We provide your USA freight forwarder a shipping invoice with item#, description, quantity, pricing, country of origin, harmonized code and estimated dims and weights&nbsp;</span><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">of each item.</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></span><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">2. The USA sales tax is based on the ship to City and State.</span><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">3. For Sales tax refund, please provide bill of lading or&nbsp;AWB&nbsp;(once available) showing that this order was exported out of the USA.<br></font></div><div><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">4. When contacting your potential Freight Forwarder, please ensure that they will be the EXPORTER of RECORD for your movement of product from the US to it's final destination.</font></div><span class="im" style="color: rgb(80, 0, 80);"><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">RH doesn't fill out the Shipper's Letter of Instruction (SLI) as we are not the&nbsp;party&nbsp;that is exporting. You (the customer) has been provide with our shipping invoice for filling out this form. &nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">In terms of documentation, RH as the&nbsp;USPPI&nbsp;(U.S.&nbsp;Principal&nbsp;<wbr>Party&nbsp;in&nbsp;Interest) will provide “Basic Commodity Information” (our name, our&nbsp;EIN&nbsp;number, U.S. Harmonized Tariff Codes, product description, product quantity, product value, product weight, product carton dimensions) in a Routed Export Transaction within 5 business days of a finalized, signed quote. RH will also provide, upon request, a “Consent to Screen” and a copy of the RH’s standard commercial invoice. You (the customer) shall be responsible for complying with all U.S. and foreign export and import laws and regulations and will obtain all required U.S. and foreign authorizations, permits or licenses with respect to the products.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Furthermore, you (the customer) shall be fully responsible for the preparation and filing of all shipping and other documentation necessary for export and import clearance.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div></div></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.3333px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not hesitate to contact us should you have any questions.</span></div><font face="arial"><br></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="gmail_default"><div dir="ltr"><div class="adL"><span class="im" style="color: rgb(80, 0, 80);"><div><table cellpadding="0" width="500" cellspacing="0" id="topTable" height="450"><tbody><tr valign="top"><td styleinsert="1" height="300"><table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400"><tbody><tr valign="top" height="400"><td teditid="c1r1" aeditid="c1r1" locked="0"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><font>Thank you,&nbsp;<br></font></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br>{!Opportunity.Price_Bid_Contact__c}<br><br>&nbsp;</font></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr valign="top"></tr></tbody></table></div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(3